    "Advertising should be scrutinized with great care.",
    "Word-of-mouth recommendations need to be accepted only from colleagues with substantial history of actual implementation.",
    "For example, Lin (2022) introduced Idi-omsTube (https:// www. idiom stube.",
    "com), a language learning tool for facilitating the learning of English idiomatic expressions from YouTube videos.",
    "This automatically: (1) assesses the speech rate and lexical difficulty level of any learner-chosen English-captioned YouTube video, (2) generates a range of vocabulary-building and revision tasks (e.g., fill-in-the-blanks, the spelling game hangman, pronunciation, flashcards), and (3) recommends YouTube videos based on learners' individual learning progress."
